response.original_title: Best of Super Crazy - Insane Luchador
response.overview: Nobody has arrived on the ECW scene that has created as much excitement as Super Crazy. He wrestling and high-flying are out of this world and extreme style is as hardcore as anybody! Witness unbelievable matches that are truly some of the most entertaining specticles scene to man! Re-live his classic feud with Yoshihiro Tajiri, his battle with the top Mexican & Japanese talent that has arrived in ECW, plus even a dream match with Jeff Hardy. Extreme Lucha Libre lives and it is in ECW! 4hrs.
response.title: Best of Super Crazy - Insane Luchador
